♪My poor words♪

67
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:17,540
♪The monsoon seems to have a destination♪

68
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:20,260
♪The clouds are moving slowly♪

69
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:24,780
♪If every time I miss you♪

70
00:03:24,780 --> 00:03:28,020
♪There will be one more star in the sky♪

71
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:31,260
♪I worry if you'd get nervous♪

72
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,480
(Next episode)
You are indeed qualified to be manager.

73
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,360
I admit it.

74
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,000
Wei Yingying.

75
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,400
Hitting on my fiancé?

76
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,880
I'll beat you up whenever I see you.

77
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,240
I am your fiancé.

78
